{"id":"the-boy-who-mapped-the-wind","slug":"the-boy-who-mapped-the-wind","title":"The Boy Who Mapped the Wind","title_ko":"바람을 그린 소년","level":"B1","ageBand":"11-13","coverUrl":"/seed/the-boy-who-mapped-the-wind/cover.webp","summary_ko":"보이지 않는 바람을 지도에 담으려는 소년이 깃발과 소리, 사람들의 생활을 관찰하는 이야기예요.","wordCount":255,"pages":[{"id":"the-boy-who-mapped-the-wind-p1","pageNo":1,"spread":"p1","imageUrl":"/seed/the-boy-who-mapped-the-wind/p1.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-boy-who-mapped-the-wind-p1-s1","ord":0,"text":"Tae wanted to draw a map of the wind, which made his classmates laugh. You cannot map what you cannot see, they said.","translation_ko":"태오는 바람 지도를 그리고 싶었고 친구들은 웃었어요. 보이지 않는 것은 지도에 그릴 수 없다고 했어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-boy-who-mapped-the-wind/audio/p1-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"Tae","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":400},{"word":"wanted","charStart":4,"charEnd":10,"startMs":400,"endMs":920},{"word":"to","charStart":11,"charEnd":13,"startMs":920,"endMs":1360},{"word":"draw","charStart":14,"charEnd":18,"startMs":1360,"endMs":1380},{"word":"a","charStart":19,"charEnd":20,"startMs":1380,"endMs":1680},{"word":"map","charStart":21,"charEnd":24,"startMs":1680,"endMs":1880},{"word":"of","charStart":25,"charEnd":27,"startMs":1880,"endMs":2120},{"word":"the","charStart":28,"charEnd":31,"startMs":2120,"endMs":2300},{"word":"wind","charStart":32,"charEnd":36,"startMs":2300,"endMs":2540},{"word":"which","charStart":38,"charEnd":43,"startMs":3080,"endMs":3160},{"word":"made","charStart":44,"charEnd":48,"startMs":3160,"endMs":3380},{"word":"his","charStart":49,"charEnd":52,"startMs":3380,"endMs":3600},{"word":"classmates","charStart":53,"charEnd":63,"startMs":3600,"endMs":4020},{"word":"laugh","charStart":64,"charEnd":69,"startMs":4020,"endMs":4460},{"word":"You","charStart":71,"charEnd":74,"startMs":5000,"endMs":5140},{"word":"cannot","charStart":75,"charEnd":81,"startMs":5140,"endMs":5460},{"word":"map","charStart":82,"charEnd":85,"startMs":5460,"endMs":5720},{"word":"what","charStart":86,"charEnd":90,"startMs":5720,"endMs":5880},{"word":"you","charStart":91,"charEnd":94,"startMs":5880,"endMs":6080},{"word":"cannot","charStart":95,"charEnd":101,"startMs":6080,"endMs":6360},{"word":"see","charStart":102,"charEnd":105,"startMs":6360,"endMs":6700},{"word":"they","charStart":107,"charEnd":111,"startMs":7020,"endMs":7200},{"word":"said","charStart":112,"charEnd":116,"startMs":7200,"endMs":7420}]}]},{"id":"the-boy-who-mapped-the-wind-p2","pageNo":2,"spread":"p2","imageUrl":"/seed/the-boy-who-mapped-the-wind/p2.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-boy-who-mapped-the-wind-p2-s1","ord":0,"text":"But Tae had seen the wind push laundry east, bend barley west, and steal hats near the bus stop. Invisible did not mean unknowable.","translation_ko":"하지만 태오는 바람이 빨래를 동쪽으로 밀고 보리를 서쪽으로 휘게 하고 버스 정류장 근처에서 모자를 훔쳐 가는 것을 보았어요. 보이지 않는다고 알 수 없는 것은 아니었어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-boy-who-mapped-the-wind/audio/p2-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"But","charStart":0,"charEnd":3,"startMs":0,"endMs":900},{"word":"Tae","charStart":4,"charEnd":7,"startMs":900,"endMs":1260},{"word":"had","charStart":8,"charEnd":11,"startMs":1260,"endMs":1700},{"word":"seen","charStart":12,"charEnd":16,"startMs":1700,"endMs":2060},{"word":"the","charStart":17,"charEnd":20,"startMs":2060,"endMs":2280},{"word":"wind","charStart":21,"charEnd":25,"startMs":2280,"endMs":2640},{"word":"push","charStart":26,"charEnd":30,"startMs":3160,"endMs":3220},{"word":"laundry","charStart":31,"charEnd":38,"startMs":3220,"endMs":3700},{"word":"east","charStart":39,"charEnd":43,"startMs":3700,"endMs":4220},{"word":"bend","charStart":45,"charEnd":49,"startMs":5160,"endMs":5220},{"word":"barley","charStart":50,"charEnd":56,"startMs":5220,"endMs":5640},{"word":"west","charStart":57,"charEnd":61,"startMs":5640,"endMs":6180},{"word":"and","charStart":63,"charEnd":66,"startMs":6960,"endMs":7160},{"word":"steal","charStart":67,"charEnd":72,"startMs":7160,"endMs":7500},{"word":"hats","charStart":73,"charEnd":77,"startMs":7500,"endMs":7900},{"word":"near","charStart":78,"charEnd":82,"startMs":7900,"endMs":8140},{"word":"the","charStart":83,"charEnd":86,"startMs":8140,"endMs":8340},{"word":"bus","charStart":87,"charEnd":90,"startMs":8340,"endMs":8500},{"word":"stop","charStart":91,"charEnd":95,"startMs":8500,"endMs":8840},{"word":"Invisible","charStart":97,"charEnd":106,"startMs":10000,"endMs":10320},{"word":"did","charStart":107,"charEnd":110,"startMs":10320,"endMs":11020},{"word":"not","charStart":111,"charEnd":114,"startMs":11020,"endMs":11340},{"word":"mean","charStart":115,"charEnd":119,"startMs":11340,"endMs":11720},{"word":"unknowable","charStart":120,"charEnd":130,"startMs":11720,"endMs":12360}]}]},{"id":"the-boy-who-mapped-the-wind-p3","pageNo":3,"spread":"p3","imageUrl":"/seed/the-boy-who-mapped-the-wind/p3.webp","sentences":[{"id":"the-boy-who-mapped-the-wind-p3-s1","ord":0,"text":"He tied red ribbons to fences and blue ribbons to tree branches. Then he watched which ones danced first each morning.","translation_ko":"태오는 울타리에 빨간 리본을, 나뭇가지에 파란 리본을 묶었어요. 그리고 아침마다 어느 리본이 먼저 춤추는지 보았어요.","audioUrl":"/seed/the-boy-who-mapped-the-wind/audio/p3-s1.mp3","wordTimings":[{"word":"He","charStart":0,"charEnd":2,"startMs":0,"endMs":180},{"word":"tied","charStart":3,"charEnd":7,"startMs":180,"endMs":460},{"word":"red","charStart":8,"charEnd":11,"startMs":460,"endMs":860},{"word":"ribbons","charStart":12,"charEnd":19,"startMs":860,"endMs":1100},{"word":"to","charStart":20,"charEnd":22,"startMs":1100,"endMs":1460},{"word":"fences","charStart":23,"charEnd":29,"startMs":1460,"endMs":1720},{"word":"and","charStart":30,"charEnd":33,"startMs":1720,"endMs":2480},{"word":"blue","charStart":34,"charEnd":38,"startMs":2480,"endMs":2740},{"word":"ribbons","charStart":39,"charEnd":46,"startMs":2740,"endMs":2960},{"word":"to","charStart":47,"charEnd":49,"startMs":2960,"endMs":3360},{"word":"tree","charStart":50,"charEnd":54,"startMs":3360,"endMs":3520},{"word":"branches","charStart":55,"charEnd":63,"